citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:10 pm to 1:45 pm
on October 2, 2023. Inspector knocked on front door, left voicemail at phone number on file, left phone message at place
of employment and waited 30 minutes.
End Section
